# Component and Hook Patterns

- Components in `src/` use named exports; screens in `app/` use default export.
- Define a props interface for every component; do not use `any`.
- Keep data fetching in hooks/services, not directly in presentational components.
- Hook naming: `useXxx`; return object shape for readability.
- Use memoization patterns (`React.memo`, `useCallback`, `useMemo`) when needed.
